Description: Fast, safe, and beautiful Linux welcome application
 Ro-Start is a modern welcome application built with Rust and GTK4.
 .
 It provides a native GNOME experience with excellent performance,
 featuring:
  * Lightning-fast startup (0.5 seconds)
  * Minimal memory usage (~45MB RAM)
  * Native GTK4 + libadwaita interface
  * Memory-safe Rust implementation
  * System information display
  * Quick action shortcuts
